<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="show-n">show <strong><em>n</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /ʃəʊ/    美 /ʃoʊ/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>演出；表演；(广播 / 电视) 节目：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The theatre gives two shows in one day.
这家剧场一天演出两场。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a <strong>quiz show</strong>
智力竞赛节目</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>展览 (会)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The designer clothes will be <strong>on show</strong> in Chicago next month.
这些名牌服装将于下个月在芝加哥展出。</p></div></div>